Ok, I'm back and half asleep. If ya see a bunch of 'Z's, it means I'm 
sleeping on the keyboard.

Sorry to anyone who I delayed, I only got a few mins online yesterday 
and had to go pretty quick.

::WarMachine/Bloodystrike/DevilDuer::

WarMachine jumps to the side, the missiles passing him by a few 
inches. Roaring he returns fire, his first several shots and one 
missile missing Shokaract as he hits the ground, but the rest heading 
right for the bot.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DevilDuer raises an eyebrow, looking back at Diamond. "Good thing I 
didn't decide to attack you..." he says in reply to the information 
on her acid.

He takes a step back, motioning for Diamond to proceed. "Go right 
ahead, I think she'd be better if she was relaxed."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Bloodystrike frowns as Life walks out, running after him.

"Hey, wait up! Who're you looking for??"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
